        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "It's seven o'clock in the morning, and it's time to get up.Listen and circle.\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            455,
            395,
            2232,
            525
          ],
          "block_id": 1,
          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "1. Who are the people talking?A. Doctors.B.Parents.",
          "block_bbox": [
            461,
            554,
            1411,
            671
          ],
          "block_id": 2,
          "block_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "2. What are they talking about?\nA. Going to the zoo.B. Going to school.",
          "block_bbox": [
            461,
            706,
            1610,
            823
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "Let's talk ",
          "block_bbox": [
            471,
            877,
            896,
            951
          ],
          "block_id": 4,
          "block_order": 5
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
          "block_content": "zoo \n,\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            1419,
            781,
            2386,
            1892
          ],
          "block_id": 5,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "Mum: Sarah, Sam, come here, please.Sarah: What's wrong?\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            310,
            994,
            1345,
            1125
          ],
          "block_id": 6,
          "block_order": 6
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "Mum: Your father is ill.He should see a doctor this morning,so we can't go to the zoo today.\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            337,
            1149,
            1399,
            1364
          ],
          "block_id": 7,
          "block_order": 7
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "Sam: Oh,no!",
          "block_bbox": [
            343,
            1386,
            694,
            1437
          ],
          "block_id": 8,
          "block_order": 8
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "Mum: Don't be sad.We can go next time.",
          "block_bbox": [
            330,
            1465,
            1427,
            1520
          ],
          "block_id": 9,
          "block_order": 9
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "Sam:How does Dad feel now?",
          "block_bbox": [
            338,
            1544,
            1148,
            1595
          ],
          "block_id": 10,
          "block_order": 10
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "Mum: Not well.Let's go to the hospital.Howdoes Samfeel? What should hedo?\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            327,
            1621,
            1378,
            1829
          ],
          "block_id": 11,
          "block_order": 11
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "Act with your friends.",
          "block_bbox": [
            439,
            1884,
            1111,
            1943
          ],
          "block_id": 12,
          "block_order": 12
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "Your friends need some help.Call them and give your suggestions.",
          "block_bbox": [
            435,
            1955,
            2183,
            2014
          ],
          "block_id": 13,
          "block_order": 13
        },
        {
          "block_label": "image",
          "block_content": "you \nDon't be angry.\n\nYou should take a \n\ndeep breath.\n\nI'm \n\n60angry.\n\n",
