      "markdown": "## Let's try \n\nIt's seven o'clock in the morning, and it's time to get up.Listen and circle.\n\n\n\n1. Who are the people talking?A. Doctors.B.Parents.\n\n2. What are they talking about?\n\nA. Going to the zoo.B. Going to school.\n\n## Let's talk \n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_1419_781_2386_1892.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"38%\" /></div>\n\n\nMum: Sarah, Sam, come here, please.Sarah: What's wrong?\n\n\n\nMum: Your father is ill.He should see a doctor this morning,so we can't go to the zoo today.\n\n\n\nSam: Oh,no!\n\nMum: Don't be sad.We can go next time.\n\nSam:How does Dad feel now?\n\nMum: Not well.Let's go to the hospital.Howdoes Samfeel? What should hedo?\n\n\n\nAct with your friends.\n\nYour friends need some help.Call them and give your suggestions.\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_242_2036_1992_2793.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"70%\" /></div>\n",
